            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h2 id=\"key-insights\">Key Insights</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Iran hosts the most refugees at 3.49 million, primarily from Afghanistan</li>\n<li>Uganda (1.76M) and Chad (1.28M) host more refugees than far wealthier nations</li>\n<li>Germany (2.75M) and Poland (1.01M) are the top European hosts, driven by Syria and Ukraine crises</li>\n<li>The top 20 host countries collectively shelter over 20 million refugees</li>\n</ul></span>"
